<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;">  promotional_text</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">: </span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;Now with diagonal-X support.&quot;</span></span>
